data.description: Welcome to the beautiful Phillips Trace Community! This beautiful home features hardwoods in the spacious entryway that leads to the formal dining room, which could also functions as a home office or flex space. Granite countertops, lots of cabinets, and recessed lighting are all features of the spacious kitchen! After a long day enjoy your fireside family room ideal for hosting guests.  Relax in your enormous owner's suite  which has a spacious sitting area, vaulted ceiling, a spa-like bathroom with two vanities, and large  walk-in closet!  10k in Closing cost with full price offer.
